      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and looking for a great new home! It's been well-loved and well-maintained, so you're getting a fantastic vehicle. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 28900.0,
