    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 996-generation Carrera 4S, featuring the legendary 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This wide-body example retains its factory-spec AWD system and enhanced braking components derived from the Turbo. Significant preventative maintenance has been completed, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The suspension remains taut with updated Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis communicates every nuance of the road. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, with a linear power band and crisp synchros throughout the gear range.",
      "price": 36500.0,
