    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery is in great shape, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat entry bolster, while the dashboard and door panels remain free of cracks or sun damage. All interior technology, including the infotainment screen and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance during my ownership to provide total peace of mind for the next owner. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready to be driven home today.",
